devdoc.details: Implements secure deposit and withdrawal mechanisms with limits

params.user: Address of the user who made the deposit
Address of the user who made the withdrawal

params._bankCap: Maximum total amount that can be deposited in the bank
params._withdrawalLimit: Maximum amount that can be withdrawn in a single transaction

deposit().details: Emits a Deposit event on success

returns._0: The remaining capacity that can be deposited
The balance of the specified user

withdraw(uint256).details: Follows checks-effects-interactions pattern and emits a Withdrawal event on success

bankCap.details: This value is immutable and set during contract deployment

withdrawalLimit.details: This value is immutable and set during contract deployment
